short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A demonstration of how accessibility analytics data capture could work on any webpage or website.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension simulates the capturing of accessibility specific info as part of web analytics. 

It does not actually do this, nor does it send the information it captures anywhere. The only destination of the captured information is your Console's output in DevTools.
